      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with this absolute beauty, but it's time for her to find a new home where she'll be just as cherished. I\u2019ve babied this car since the moment I got it\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed with love every weekend. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Aside from maybe a tiny, barely-there mark from a stray pebble (hey, that's just a bit of character, right?), she is truly pristine. It drives like a dream and catches eyes everywhere. Come on over, let's chat cars, and see why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
